How to Use This Project Legally:

If you want to use this portfolio as a template:

1. Fork or clone this repository
2. Replace ALL personal content with your own:
     - Update src/config/site.ts with your information
     - Replace images in public/ with your own photos
     - Update all content in src/messages/ folders
     - Rewrite all blog posts and personal descriptions
3. You may keep or modify the code structure under the MIT License
4. Give appropriate credit (optional but appreciated)

